Rift Valley fever, South Africa
----------------------------
Information received on 7 May 2010 from Mr Bothle Michael Modisane,
Chief Director Food and Veterinary Services, Department of
Agriculture, Food Safety and Biosecurity: Department of Agriculture,
PRETORIA, South Africa

Summary

Report type: Follow-up report No. 8
Start date 19 Jan 2010
Date of 1st confirmation of the event 18 Feb 2010
Report date 6 May 2010
Date submitted to OIE 7 May 2010
Reason for notification: Reoccurrence of a listed disease
Date of previous occurrence 1 Jan 2010
Manifestation of disease: Clinical disease
Causal agent: Rift Valley fever virus
Nature of diagnosis: Clinical, Laboratory (advanced), Necropsy
This event pertains to the whole country

Related reports: Immediate notification (19 Feb 2010)
